#

Pork Stir-Fry with Vegetables

25 min
$12.99
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

Asian

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

QuickHealthyFamily-Friendly

Description

A quick, colorful stir-fry bursting with flavor and nutrients, perfect for any night of the week.

Ingredients

  • pork tenderloin: 1 pound
  • bell peppers: 2, sliced
  • broccoli florets: 1 cup
  • carrots: 1 cup, julienned
  • snap peas: 1 cup
  • soy sauce: 3 tablespoons
  • ginger, grated: 1 tablespoon
  • garlic, minced: 2 cloves
  • vegetable oil: 2 tablespoons
  • sesame oil: 1 teaspoon
